VALUES ("Secretlab Titan 2020 Series","The larger cousin of the Secretlab OMEGA. The Secretlab TITAN is renowned for its ample space in addition to customization at the highest level. To give you greater comfort, support, reliability and personalization, the new 2020 Series features multiple improvements that will exceed the expectations of even the most discerning. For an uncompromising experience that lasts for endless hours, this elite award-winning chair is unquestionably the gold standard you need.","img/PID1.png",99,1);
